<carm_agobard. 1.1>	Arvi polique creator inmense,
<carm_agobard. 1.2>	Qui tuum globum dimensus es palmo,
<carm_agobard. 1.3>	Tellurem cunctam pugillo concludis,
<carm_agobard. 1.4>	Fabe placatus.
<carm_agobard. 2.1>	Gnari nam probi praeinstruunt cunctos,
<carm_agobard. 2.2>	Constare nullum latibulum reo,
<carm_agobard. 2.3>	Quia tu testis et iudex ubique
<carm_agobard. 2.4>	Adesses ultor.
<carm_agobard. 3.1>	O deus sancte, depromunt examen
<carm_agobard. 3.2>	Nimis pavendum restare superbis,
<carm_agobard. 3.3>	Labentia quaeque atroci puniri
<carm_agobard. 3.4>	Acervitate.
<carm_agobard. 4.1>	Bibrant coruscae, iam sicca procumbit,
<carm_agobard. 4.2>	Tetrum puniri reatum prospectant,
<carm_agobard. 4.3>	Sed pius iudex leniri se monet
<carm_agobard. 4.4>	Actibus bonis.
<carm_agobard. 5.1>	Artor addictus larbalibus suasis
<carm_agobard. 5.2>	Horridae mortis in carcerem trusus,
<carm_agobard. 5.3>	Posco ne pandant clibani se fauces,
<carm_agobard. 5.4>	Me renitente.
<carm_agobard. 6.1>	Rumpe iam, quaeso, altitonans alme,
<carm_agobard. 6.2>	Nex pollinctoris convinxit me lege,
<carm_agobard. 6.3>	Adsis paratus et promptus ablutor,
<carm_agobard. 6.4>	O salutator.
<carm_agobard. 7.1>	Defluit vita et affluit noxa,
<carm_agobard. 7.2>	Noxae exactor pro foribus pulsat,
<carm_agobard. 7.3>	Vanam proritat, inlecebrat mentem
<carm_agobard. 7.4>	Male devinctam.
<carm_agobard. 8.1>	Opperit oram terribilem nimis,
<carm_agobard. 8.2>	Qua spiritus linquat carneam sedem,
<carm_agobard. 8.3>	Quem secum gestit abducere gaudens,
<carm_agobard. 8.4>	Eheu pro dolor!
<carm_agobard. 9.1>	Pectore in imo sic pavitans volvo
<carm_agobard. 9.2>	Necem: sodalis vel pronus amator,
<carm_agobard. 9.3>	Proximus parens vel karus germanus,
<carm_agobard. 9.4>	Opitulentur.
<carm_agobard. 10.1>	Arcent delicta scandere excelsa,
<carm_agobard. 10.2>	Animam foedam caelicolae spernunt,
<carm_agobard. 10.3>	Frigidam carnem odibilem effert
<carm_agobard. 10.4>	Karus superstes.
<carm_agobard. 11.1>	Xriste tu solus omnimoda ope
<carm_agobard. 11.2>	Viribus vitam et requie mortem
<carm_agobard. 11.3>	Robora, sensum et conplue rore
<carm_agobard. 11.4>	Aeternitatis.
<carm_agobard. 12.1>	Suscipe, pater, versiculos missos
<carm_agobard. 12.2>	Tibi, vocaris tu vero meorum
<carm_agobard. 12.3>	In versuum primis litteris: tuum
<carm_agobard. 12.4>	Lege iam nomen.
<carm_agobard. 13.1>	Tu ut in Christo valeas, obto
<carm_agobard. 13.2>	Fratresque ut sospitet, quaero deum:
<carm_agobard. 13.3>	Ut vos quiete fruatis aeternae
<carm_agobard. 13.4>	Lucis, exoro.
<carm_agobard. 14.1>	Tu quoque meis sic annue votis,
<carm_agobard. 14.2>	Ut me commendes christicolis notis,
<carm_agobard. 14.3>	Quis det, ut velit redemptor me celsus
<carm_agobard. 14.4>	Iungere suis.
<carm_agobard. 15.1>	Praestet hoc sanctus ingenitus auctor,
<carm_agobard. 15.2>	Geniti pater et prolis quoaevus,
<carm_agobard. 15.3>	Quibus non dispar spiritus constat
<carm_agobard. 15.4>	In saecula amen.